item.title: Barrelmanboy - Miniature Minorities [Project, WIP, Remixable]
item.dc:creator: Barrelmanboy
item.description:
Actually, I will upload it. I won’t take all the credit, obviously. I can title it like “Barrelmanboy & Fokkses - Miniature Minorities.” Actually, hearing it back now, I might change the name to suit the theme of the song, whatever the theme actually is. First, I’ll upload it to YouTube as an untitled project, and ask everyone who watches what a good name would be. The one I find fitting will be used, and I’ll then upload it to SoundCloud. I’ll probably repost it to YouTube with that name, though. I won’t make any of this a reality until you agree on it. So it’s up to you to decide whether I upload or I don’t upload.
